{"type":"message","id":"4317629c","parentId":"df8678c5","timestamp":"2026-05-10T11:34:39.853Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Oq8FYxJzE3GbxPqxlgTDOJA7|fc_0b723d20877b61e0016a006d4324248191a3e1bdf45e108342","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5d5cfc289d8ac77f5dfdac0b4141764ae1392a9c5d4eb8fe1640fcc1b737ca48\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 32,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7073245305340025,\n      \"snippet\": \"# MEMORY.md - Long-term Memory\\n\\n## Identity\\n- Name: Owen (โอเว่น) — Personal AI Secretary\\n- Boss: robberzaz (Telegram @Owenzzz_bot, ID: 1060942816)\\n- Language: Thai only\\n\\n## Technical Config\\n- OpenClaw: systemd user service (auto-start)\\n- Hermes: systemd user service (auto-start)\\n- Primary model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\\n- Fallbacks: ollama-pay/deepseek-v4-pro:cloud, ollama-pay/gemini-3-flash-preview:cloud, ollama-pay/qwen3.5:397b-cloud\\n- Provider: thaigq (https://ollama-pay.thaigqsoft.com/api/v1)\\n- tools.exec.ask = off (YOLO mode)\\n- commands.ownerAllowFrom = [1060942816]\\n- Code work: use SocratiCode first\\n\\n## Critical Commands (NEVER FORGET)\\n\\n1. **/model shows 200+ models fix:**\\n   `openclaw co\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L1-L32\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L1-L32\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ec95d16286b79164ff7d818edebc3ec5c0656dc8d630ffd91e389a9a72a386eb\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 59,\n      \"endLine\": 61,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.6658401155412546,\n      \"snippet\": \"- 2026-05-10: Preferred compact reply format: top line only `🧑🏼‍💻[GPT 5.5] [ทำงาน/คำถามทั่วไป/สรุป] 🧑🏼‍💻`; do not show token numbers or token level in the top prefix. Put token status at the very bottom before the closing emoji, e.g. `[Tokens: น้อย | Cache: 68% | RTK: ไม่ใช้]`. Must call `session_status` before replying when feasible to calculate the level; if unavailable, write `[Tokens: unavailable]`. Token level rules: น้อย ≤25% context or ≤35k input, ปกติ 26-45% or 35k-70k, สูง 46-70% or 70k-120k, สูงมาก >70% or >120k; use the higher level if signals conflict. In ทำงาน mode, >70k input or >45% context must warn about possible hidden context/tool output; >120k input or >70% context\\n\\nSource: MEMORY.md#L59-L61\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"MEMORY.md#L59-L61\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"be340cc60afde1eb614663b22dee06c33568502ca336b8f2991229f79f5d5a17\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/archive/2026-05-07.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 10,\n      \"endLine\": 23,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.5930319269938801,\n      \"snippet\": \"- แก้ถาวรโดย backup `~/.hermes/config.yaml`, ลบ allowlist ที่อนุญาตคำสั่ง restart/kill Hermes gateway ออกจาก `command_allowlist`, ตั้ง `resume_pending=false` ใน `~/.hermes/sessions/sessions.json`, restart Hermes หนึ่งครั้งเพื่อโหลด config ใหม่; health OK และ `hermes-gateway-comfyui.service` ยัง disabled/inactive\\n\\n## create-face-portrait / ComfyUI analysis\\n- อ่านสกิล `create-face-portrait` ด้วย SocratiCode แล้วพบว่า flow จริงอยู่ที่ `scripts/create_face_portrait.py` + `references/face_portrait_workflow.json`\\n- workflow ชี้ checkpoint `flux1-dev-fp8.safetensors` ถูกแล้ว แต่สคริปต์ล็อก node id ตายตัว (`workflow[\\\"6\\\"]`, `workflow[\\\"9\\\"]`) ทำให้เปราะถ้า workflow เปลี่ยน\\n- `SKILL.md` อ้างว่ามี `--neg\\n\\nSource: memory/archive/2026-05-07.md#L10-L23\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/archive/2026-05-07.md#L10-L23\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"4fc0cd536a2edb5f26a764491272c1f57175152c487f00849ff2a8453d0dea1a\",\n      \"path\": \"MEMORY.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 39,\n      \"endLine\": 58,\n      \"score\": 0.9537808582717991,\n      \"textScore\": 0.32189406581896896,\n      \"